_sText:
Medium difficulty zombie escape map for CS-Source

3 stages so far (hope to add 2 more in the future)
 - 1 stage based on "Willy's Wonderland (2021)" movie
 - 1 stage based on "As above, So Below (2014)" movie
 - 1 stage based on "Harry Potter 3" (using assets from the 2nd game)

Each stage is about 8-9 minutes. There are NPC-s and zombie items
